- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): The paper uses symbolic expressions as an abstraction of the program, which is a topic related to logic in computer science. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory): The paper proposes a new formalization of functor domains, which is a topic related to formal languages and automata theory. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper presents a complete analyzer for embedded C programs, which is a topic related to systems and control.
